This became the first major breakthrough.

Filesystem MCP behaved differently from Scholarship MCP.

---

# 11.11 Engineering Observation

Question

Why would one Local MCP work

while another Local MCP fail?

Both use

```
STDIO
```

Therefore

STDIO itself was not the issue.

The difference had to exist somewhere else.

---

# 11.12 Root Cause Investigation

Scholarship MCP

```
Python
```

Filesystem MCP

```
Node.js

↓

npm

↓

npx
```

This revealed the hidden dependency.

The issue was not

MCP.

The issue was

Runtime.

